CONTEXT LeftResidualComposition2 IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT LeftResidualComposition2
{+ This test verifies left residual works in reverse composition context. +}

CLASSIFY A ISA B

RELATION r[W*B]
RELATION s[Z*B]
RELATION t[Z*X]
RELATION result[W*X]

RULE testLeftResidualComposition2: result = (r/s);t

ENDCONTEXT
